vars: { d2-config: { layout-engine: elk } }
direction: right

title: |md
  ## JI as-is database schema — overview
  46 production tables in 6 areas · inter-area FK relationships aggregated (edge label = count) · 0 explicit FK constraints in source DDL
| { near: top-center; style.font-size: 22 }

